# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .dockerignore
#
# Like .gitignore but for Docker. Files listed here are NOT copied
# into the Docker image during `docker build`.
#
# WHY THIS MATTERS:
#   - node_modules: Docker installs its own (for Linux/alpine OS).
#     Copying your local node_modules (built for Mac/Windows) would
#     cause crashes inside the Linux container.
#   - .env: NEVER bake secrets into Docker images. Pass them via
#     environment variables at runtime.
#   - logs: Container should write fresh logs, not inherit old ones.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

node_modules
npm-debug.log
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
logs
*.log
.git
.gitignore
README.md
ecosystem.config.js
